    public interface DecoratedManagedObject
extends DecoratedPersistenceObject, com.ericsson.oss.itpf.datalayer.dps.persistence.LockableManagedObject
    Extends the public managed object interface with methods that are used internally by DPS but are not to be exposed externally to clients.
